{"tid":1270100,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知大家有冇聽過新界六日戰","createTime":"2019-06-30T18:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T19:11:46.000Z","uid":45622,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"36261a4f80ed279661f4ce67bf4792e8a59d3e9d","tid":1270100,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:27:58.000Z","msg":"呢件事發生係英屬香港嘅時期<br />\n雖然一邊係大家好鐘意嘅英國人<br />\n另一邊係大家好唔鐘意嘅新界牛屎佬<br />\n但係撇除呢d野<br />\n只講班牛屎佬為咗保護自己地方<br />\n保護自己應得嘅野<br />\n保護自己嘅將來<br />\n可以自發組織一班人出黎對抗一班軍人<br />\n雖然最尾都係失敗收場<br />\n仲要死咗五百人<br />\n但係佢地都企過出黎抗爭<br />\n亦換黎後代嘅安穩<br />\n即係現在個個屌嘅丁權<br />\n<br />\n加油 香港"},{"pid":"d185ebb54ab81c3b9ebccb56cf9ea096dec8936a","tid":1270100,"uid":66270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:29:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd18c77a3512caa73692b55c458c5b60006f4ca3","tid":1270100,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:44:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6f75ba880fc7c892753866d4480f0000a7151c86","tid":1270100,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"利申返<br />\n學術討論<br />\n研究下勇武抗爭可以換黎d咩"},{"pid":"eb4e1644b5d260039eb083cde76c017ed9b2fda5","tid":1270100,"uid":219614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f75ba880fc7c892753866d4480f0000a7151c86","tid":1270100,"uid":45622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"利申返<br />\n學術討論<br />\n研究下勇武抗爭可以換黎d咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T19:11:46.000Z","msg":"中共點建國?<br />\n清朝點比人推翻?"}]}